---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Anton Meier Ebsen Jørgensen – Ressourcer & Downloads" 
  description="Gratis ressourcer og downloads: Excel-skabeloner, kode, noter og guides."
  bodyClass="resources-page"
>
<style>
.resources-wrap {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 24px auto;
  padding: 0 16px 32px;
}

.card {
  background: var(--glass);
  backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 24px;
  border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1), border-color 0.3s ease;
}
.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.01);
  border-color: var(--accent-soft);
}

.section-title {
  margin: 0 0 24px;
  font-size: 13px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--accent);
}

.eyebrow {
  margin: 0 0 12px;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  font-weight: 800;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  font-size: 12px;
}

.lead { 
  margin: 0 0 24px; 
  color: var(--text-dim); 
  font-size: 18px; 
  line-height: 1.6; 
}

.muted { 
  color: var(--text-dim); 
  opacity: 0.7; 
}
.small { 
  font-size: 13px; 
}

.cta {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 10px;
  margin: 10px 0 14px;
}

.btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: var(--accent);
  color: #050506;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 14.5px;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
}
.btn:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: var(--glow);
}
.btn.ghost {
  background: transparent;
  border: 1.5px solid var(--accent);
  color: var(--accent);
}

.pill-wrap {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 8px;
  margin-top: 8px;
}

.pill {
  padding: 6px 14px;
  background: var(--accent-soft);
  border: 1px solid var(--accent);
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  color: var(--accent);
}

/* Hero */
.hero {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.6fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
  gap: 22px;
  align-items: start;
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.mini-card {
  background: var(--glass);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border-radius: 14px;
  padding: 16px;
  border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
}
.mini-card:hover { 
  border-color: var(--accent-soft); 
}

/* Downloads grid */
.dl-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0,1fr));
  gap: 14px;
  margin-top: 12px;
}

.dl {
  border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 16px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
}

.dl-top {
  display: flex;
  gap: 10px;
  align-items: flex-start;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.dl-title {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.25;
}

.tag {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  padding: 4px 10px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  border: 1px solid var(--accent-blue);
  background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
  color: var(--accent-blue);
  white-space: nowrap;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.dl-meta {
  margin: 0 0 10px;
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--text-dim);
}

.dl-actions {
  margin-top: 12px;
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 10px;
}

/* Mobile */
@media (max-width: 980px) {
  .hero { 
    grid-template-columns: 1fr; 
  }
  .dl-grid { 
    grid-template-columns: 1fr; 
  }
}

.resources-wrap > .card {
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.resources-wrap > .card:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}
</style>

  <main class="resources-wrap">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="card hero">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Ressourcer</p>
        <h1>Downloads & templates</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Små, praktiske ressourcer jeg selv bruger: skabeloner, cheat sheets og eksempler.
          Alt er lavet til at være plug-and-play.
        </p>

        <div class="pill-wrap">
          <span class="pill">Excel</span>
          <span class="pill">VBA</span>
          <span class="pill">Python</span>
          <span class="pill">SAS</span>
          <span class="pill">GAMS</span>
        </div>

        <div class="cta">
          <a class="btn" href="#downloads">Se downloads</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="/kursusstatistik">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-column"></i> Se kursusstatistik
          </a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="/contact">Spørg om noget specifikt</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-side">
        <div class="mini-card">
          <h2 class="section-title">Note</h2>
          <p class="muted small">
            Nogle filer kan være “sanitized” (fjernet data/navne) pga. kursus/fortrolighed.
          </p>
          <p class="muted small" style="margin-top:10px;">
            Har du et konkret behov? Skriv — jeg kan ofte lave en skabelon, der passer.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- DOWNLOADS -->
    <section class="card" id="downloads">
      <h2 class="section-title">Downloads</h2>
      <p class="muted">Placér filer i mappen <code>assets/downloads/</code> og link dem her.</p>

      <div class="dl-grid">

        <!-- NEW: Kursusstatistik -->
        <article class="dl" id="dl-kursusstatistik">
          <div class="dl-top">
            <h3 class="dl-title">Kursusstatistik: evalueringer & nøgletal</h3>
            <span class="tag">Undervisning</span>
          </div>
          <p class="dl-meta">Webside · opdateret: (indsæt dato)</p>
          <p class="muted">
            Overblik over kursusevalueringer og statistik på tværs af hold. Kort, konkret og let at skimme.
          </p>
          <div class="dl-actions">
            <a class="btn" href="/kursusstatistik">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> Se side
            </a>

            <!-- VALGFRI: hvis du lægger Excel-filen i assets/downloads/ -->
            <a class="btn ghost" href="/assets/downloads/kursusevalueringer-statistik.xlsx" download>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i> Download data
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Download card 1 -->
        <article class="dl">
          <div class="dl-top">
            <h3 class="dl-title">Excel: Budget & model-skabelon</h3>
            <span class="tag">Excel</span>
          </div>
          <p class="dl-meta">Template · opdateret: (indsæt dato)</p>
          <p class="muted">En ren skabelon til struktur: inputs, beregninger, output, checks og scenarier.</p>
          <div class="dl-actions">
            <a class="btn" href="/assets/downloads/excel-template.xlsx" download>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i> Download
            </a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="#" aria-disabled="true">Beskrivelse</a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Download card 2 -->
        <article class="dl">
          <div class="dl-top">
            <h3 class="dl-title">VBA: Snippets (hurtige genveje)</h3>
            <span class="tag">VBA</span>
          </div>
          <p class="dl-meta">ZIP/tekst · opdateret: (indsæt dato)</p>
          <p class="muted">Korte code blocks: import/cleaning, formatting, loops, performance tips.</p>
          <div class="dl-actions">
            <a class="btn" href="/assets/downloads/vba-snippets.zip" download>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i> Download
            </a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="https://github.com/AntonEbsen" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <i class="fa-brands fa-github"></i> GitHub
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Download card 3 -->
        <article class="dl">
          <div class="dl-top">
            <h3 class="dl-title">Python: Data-cleaning checklist</h3>
            <span class="tag">Python</span>
          </div>
          <p class="dl-meta">PDF · opdateret: (indsæt dato)</p>
          <p class="muted">En praktisk tjekliste til reproducérbar data prep (missing, outliers, splits, logs).</p>
          <div class="dl-actions">
            <a class="btn" href="/assets/downloads/python-checklist.pdf" download>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i> Download
            </a>
            <a class="btn ghost" href="#" aria-disabled="true">Se eksempel</a>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="card">
      <h2 class="section-title">Vil du have noget specifikt?</h2>
      <p class="muted">
        Hvis du fortæller mig dit format (Excel/Python/SAS) og mål (fx forecasting, dashboards, data-cleaning),
        kan jeg foreslå en template-struktur, der passer.
      </p>
      <div class="cta">
        <a class="btn" href="/contact">Kontakt</a>
        <a class="btn ghost" href="/services">Se services</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
